===Big River===
The Big River nation numbered 400 – 500 people consisting of five clans. Little is known of their seasonal movements although it is believed that four of the five clans moved through Oyster Bay territory along the [[River Derwent (Tasmania)|Derwent River]] to reach their coastal camps near [[Midway Point, Tasmania|Pitt Water]]. The Oyster Bay People had reciprocal movement rights through Big River territory.{{sfn|Refshauge|1804}}
