* Historical novel ''[[Doctor Wooreddy's Prescription for Enduring the Ending of the World]]'' by [[Mudrooroo]]
* The poem ''Oyster Cove'' by [[Gwen Harwood]]
* The [[Australian Film Institute Award|AFI Award]]-winning [[1980 in film|1980 film]] ''[[Manganinnie]]'', based on Beth Roberts's novel.
* The Novel ''The Roving party'' by Rohan Wilson - fictional account of Manarlagenna and William "Black Bill" Ponsonby during the Black War.{{sfn|Wilson|2011}}

