{{Infobox company | name = Mobilis | logo =ATM Mobilis.svg | type = [[Società per Azioni|SPA]] | foundation = 2003 | location_city = [[Algiers]] | location_country = [[Algeria]] | industry = [[Telecommunication]]s | products = | owner = [[Algérie Télécom]] | operating_income = | net_income = | num_employees = | subsid = | homepage = http://www.mobilis.dz/ }} '''Mobilis''', or '''ATM Mobilis''' (Algeria Telecom Mobile), a subsidiary of [[Algérie Télécom]], is one of the three major mobile operators in Algeria. Mobilis, which became independent in August 2003, offers its customers: post and pre-paid offers, SMS / MMS, international roaming, voicemail, Internet billing, free notification of the balance after each call, free call to One or more favorite numbers.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.mobilis.dz/apropos.php|title=Mobilis|last=Mobilis|website=www.mobilis.dz|access-date=2017-09-07}}</ref>
