==Accidents and incidents== *On 9 April 1958, a [[Vickers Viscount]] of [[Cubana de Aviación]] was hijacked en route from [[José Martí International Airport]], [[Havana]] to [[Abel Santa Maria Airport|Santa Clara Airport]]. The aircraft landed at Mérida-Rejón Airport, [[Mexico]] where the hijack ended.<ref name=ASN090458>{{cite web|url=http://aviation-safety.net/database/record.php?id=19580409-0 |title=Accident description |publisher=Aviation Safety Network |accessdate=8 September 2009}}</ref>
