{{italic title}} '''''Oran socialiste''''' was a weekly newspaper published from [[Oran]], [[Algeria]], 1928-1939. ''Oran socialiste'' was the organ of the [[French Section of the Workers International]] (S.F.I.O.) in Oran.<ref>Ayache, Albert. ''[https://www.jstor.org/pss/3807054 Essai sur la vie syndicale en Algérie, l'année du Centenaire (1930)]''. 1972</ref><ref>[[Labour and Socialist International]]. ''The Socialist Press - The press of the parties affiliated to the Labour and Socialist International''. Series 4 - No. 2. [[Brussels]], August 1939. p. 39</ref> ''Oran socialiste'' was founded and edited by [[Marius Dubois]].<ref>''[http://www.assemblee-nationale.fr/sycomore/fiche.asp?num_dept=2624 Marius, Casimir DUBOIS DIT MARIUS-DUBOIS (1890 - 1976)]''</ref><ref>''[http://maitron-en-ligne.univ-paris1.fr/spip.php?article23064&id_mot=143 DUBOIS Marius, Casimir, dit MARIUS-DUBOIS]''</ref>
