'''Rinaldo Del Bo''' (or Dino Del Bo; 19 November 1916 – 16 January 1991) was an [[Politics of Italy|Italian politician]] who served in the [[High Authority of the European Coal and Steel Community|High Authority of the]] [[European Coal and Steel Community]], serving as President of the body between 9 October 1963 and 1967 as the [[Del Bo Authority]].

